    },
    "Whoop primary" : {

    },
    "WHOOP straps don't appear in macOS System Settings → Bluetooth. They advertise on a custom profile that only apps like NOOP can find — so there's nothing to pair there, and you shouldn't try." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "WHOOP-Straps erscheinen nicht in den macOS-Systemeinstellungen → Bluetooth. Sie senden über ein eigenes Profil, das nur Apps wie NOOP finden können — dort gibt es also nichts zu koppeln, und du solltest es nicht versuchen."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "WHOOP straps don't appear in macOS System Settings → Bluetooth. They advertise on a custom profile that only apps like NOOP can find — so there's nothing to pair there, and you shouldn't try."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Las correas WHOOP no aparecen en Configuración del sistema macOS → Bluetooth. Se anuncian en un perfil personalizado que sólo pueden encontrar aplicaciones como NOOP, por lo que no hay nada que emparejar allí y no deberías intentarlo."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Браслеты WHOOP не отображаются в «Системных настройках» macOS → Bluetooth. Они работают через особый профиль, который видят только приложения вроде NOOP, поэтому там нечего подключать — и пытаться не нужно."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "WHOOP straps don't appear in your %@'s Bluetooth settings. They advertise on a custom profile that only apps like NOOP can find — so there's nothing to pair there, and you shouldn't try." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
